{"tid":1714793,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【SOS】救中大，救手足","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T05:36:42.000Z","uid":63912,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"11187b7636b9f99d98946bda00fa4c93cc01d640","tid":1714793,"uid":63912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"有手足呼籲大學生係各校園當眼地方放上大（大到航拍可以影到）poster寫➡<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">SOS</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n向世界呼求救訊號，比全世界知道香港學府被暴力政權入侵緊！我地要比全世界知道香港警察執法係幾暴力幾無理，連學生都唔放過<br />\n<br />\n唔理有冇用，做左先！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港人，報仇！<br />\n<br />\n真香港人永遠支持中大-香港榮光大學！<br />\n手足唔係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b35155fe35b96b315f467c53a2ac38cf86ada1","tid":1714793,"uid":63912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"唔知得唔得，做左先<br />\n香港人一個都不能少"},{"pid":"8cac4285c286baf7d07d533fe4ab88dd979c9ff3","tid":1714793,"uid":63912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:54:12.000Z","msg":"入面有好多受傷手足 唔好放棄佢地"},{"pid":"6e06d039911c107bdbacf14d97cd8c091aab1bb8","tid":1714793,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:54:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n<br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙:bangbang::bangbang:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=PzS6fk0mmUdoDXVWrKgE98v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=6d206c61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1